{"tid":2247764,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美中緊張　華爾街日報：北京揚言拘留美國公民","createTime":"2020-10-18T06:08:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T12:13:19.000Z","uid":261647,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"0102f4059b81b8baca5320dc28c5689c9155f47c","tid":2247764,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T06:08:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202010180007.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202010180007.aspx&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPbXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=6c0e5989\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202010180007.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SMs2iXc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSMs2iXc.png&h=10266900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美中關係日益緊張，華爾街日報今天引述知情人士說法報導，中國政府官員警告美方可能拘留在中國的美國公民，回應美國司法部起訴與中共解放軍有關聯的學者。<br />\n<br />\n報導引述未具名人士說法指出，中方官員反覆且透過多方管道向美國政府代表發出警告，包括美國駐北京大使館。這些人士說，中方訊息很直白：美方應在美國法院撤銷告訴，否則在中國的美國公民可能發現自己違反中國法律。<br />\n<br />\n中國當局任意拘留外國公民早有前例可循，曾拒絕美國公民離境，在爆發外交糾紛後逮捕、起訴或對加拿大、澳洲與瑞典等國公民判刑。華府政壇許多人士將此稱作「人質外交」。"},{"pid":"8009910ea11cd0ce38c64521961cbf4c250fff93","tid":2247764,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T06:09:48.000Z","msg":"美國強烈反制：投票俾拜登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d408698bdb35ed19eaddaf480db5d647be0f7ff","tid":2247764,"uid":52942,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T06:11:10.000Z","msg":"歷史不斷重演，八國聯軍準備入黎救返d傳教士未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2bb87e055de324cd44857d30d4cce8e7154c27d","tid":2247764,"uid":18587,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T06:11:31.000Z","msg":"驚你唔做咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class